metadata.name: Status .tagged_with_all when given one tag returns the expected statuses

sql_query.sql: SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND (EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM statuses_tags WHERE statuses_tags.status_id = statuses.id AND statuses_tags.tag_id = 1167)) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC
